entries.journal_entry_description: Report to Lt. Maximilian Vox in Kadaara and give him the droid modules.
entries.journal_entry_title: Bring the Droid Modules to Lt. Maximilian Vox
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Standby for an incoming transmission from Lt. Maximilian Vox.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Good work, citizen! I'm very impressed. You are truly a credit to the Empire. Bring the droid modules to me in Kadaara.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Good work, citizen! I'm very impressed. You are truly a credit to the Empire. Bring the droid modules to me in Kadaara.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Go to Kadaara and speak with Lt. Maximilian Vox. He eagerly awaits you and the droid modules you've collected.
